These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, metal
1. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | mechanic | teacher |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | rat   | snake      |
| Transport   | roller | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, d&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | trance    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
